FT  12 NOV 93 / Technology (Worth Watching): Putting nature in the
dishwasher
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By DELLA BRADSHAW
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Soap powder-to-toothpaste specialist Colgate-Palmolive has turned to nature
to produce its latest tough-acting dishwasher powder, Palmolive Ultra.
Palmolive Ultra, which is on sale in the US, contains a cocktail of enzymes
which has been specially selected to attack dried food or ingredients which
produce particularly stubborn stains.
Colgate-Palmolive has applied for patents to cover the enzyme action, a
process which took five years to develop. Colgate-Palmolive: US, 212 310
2000.
