Companies:-
</XX>
<CO>Caradon.
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P5039 Construction Materials, NEC.
</IN>
